&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Harper Group is seeking reliable and hardworking individuals to join our &lt;strong&gt;Show Crew&lt;/strong&gt; for a short-term project supporting booth setup and teardown at the &lt;strong&gt;NY NOW trade show&lt;/strong&gt; at the Javits Center in New York City. This is a great opportunity to earn extra income while being part of a fast-paced, hands-on event environment. &lt;strong&gt;Pay is up to $28/hour.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Details:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dates Required:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;July 30th- August 1st and August 4th- August 5th&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location:&lt;/strong&gt; Javits Center, New York City&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unload &amp;amp; Transport:&lt;/strong&gt; Move pallets, fixtures, and product boxes to designated booth areas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fixture Repair:&lt;/strong&gt; Sand and paint damaged fixtures or booth walls as needed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teardown:&lt;/strong&gt; Assist with breakdown, repacking, and loading items for departure.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Collaborate with the team and adapt to shifting priorities to ensure timelines are met.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Physical Readiness:&lt;/strong&gt; Must be comfortable lifting, carrying, and being on your feet for extended periods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Punctuality &amp;amp; Reliability:&lt;/strong&gt; Show up on time and ready to contribute with a positive attitude.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Work Ethic:&lt;/strong&gt; Follow directions, work independently when needed, and stay focused on task completion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team Mentality:&lt;/strong&gt; Willingness to help with all aspects of the project—no task is too small.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Join Us?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be part of a high-energy team at one of the industry’s most exciting events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Earn competitive pay for a short-term project.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay active and engaged with physical, hands-on work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain experience in trade show operations and event logistics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Please Note:&lt;/strong&gt; Harper Group is a drug-free workplace.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-pay-transparency&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-input&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;title&quot;&gt;Hourly&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pay-range&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;$27&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;divider&quot;&gt;&amp;mdash;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;$28 USD&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

