&lt;p&gt;Harper Group is seeking&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Painting Temps&lt;/strong&gt; to assist our Show Operations team during the high-energy Show Season at &lt;strong&gt;The Javits Center&lt;/strong&gt;. In this role, you’ll be responsible for painting our massive &lt;strong&gt;7,000-square-foot tradeshow booth&lt;/strong&gt;, and you’ll need to work at a fast pace while still ensuring safety and precision. If you thrive in a fast-moving environment where efficiency and accuracy are key, we want you on our team!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Harper Group supplies ALL paint and equipment&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We ask that you are available and flexible to work four days - July 30th- August 1st&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Responsibilities:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Painting the entire 7,000 square foot tradeshow booth in a timely manor&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting with any light touch up regarding fixtures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Punctual – arrive on time at start of day&lt;/li&gt;
