&lt;li&gt;Ability to work independently to complete assigned tasks to completion after receiving proper instruction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Qualified candidates will possess:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to work 10-12 hour days, which may include late evening hours&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Willingness to ask questions if unsure of task(s) requested to complete&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work well under pressure and adaptable to rapid changes to fit the needs of the project&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to perform tasks that may involve lifting, bending, and standing for extended periods.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Travel Requirements:&amp;nbsp; Ability to get to and from The Javits Center&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
